Class TestCases1

  • java.lang.Object
    • junitTests.TestCases1

  • public class TestCases1
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    John Layson This JUnit test class is for testing my partner's created classes that can be instantiated which are Ordinary Truck, Refrigerated Truck, and Manifest. As the most basic, I will try to instantiate an item and test if the program gets the right name and values it's supposed to have.
